    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document registers the application/pkcs8-encrypted media type for the EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo type of PKCS #8.  An instance of this media type carries a single encrypted private key, BER-encoded as a single EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo value.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
